{
  "stem": "27390.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I spoke-- I played with the Polish children in the, in the, in the, in the, in the park and in the garden.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I spoke to them Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But at home, we only spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know why, but that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, children are children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Children didn't know much unless-- if they had at home talk against the Jews, so they also used to come out with the-- sometimes with antisemitic words.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But otherwise, children are children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We played together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[DRINKS] But, it's a fact that the Jews in Lodz got on better with the Germans before the war than they did Poles because, I think, of the language.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, German is similar to Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- also, they were more connected in business as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Jews had more contact with the Germans in business than with the Poles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I think that also made a big difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But things completely changed in, in the late '30s when we, we-- there was talk about the war coming.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So things completely changed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We became more friendly with the Poles because they felt we had more-- something in common against Hitler than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were waiting for the-- for the-- for the-- for the Nazis to march in, see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they kept away from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the situation completely changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first time I-- I experienced antisemitism, I was about eight years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to buy packets of coffee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, they had coupons on them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you collected enough coupons, you could take these coupons to a place and exchange them for-- for an album of labels of different kinds of animals.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
